STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Kenneth HOUSEKNECHT, Defendant-Movant. M-985/986 September Term 2018
082466 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a reply brief (M-986) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for direct certification (M-985) is denied.
